cking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7167e8b7624728c7808e26028c1da5c4e90e4506","tid":1016294,"uid":18692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:49:33.000Z","msg":"AAF一季都打唔完就執咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"964ebc77b404a754598af3d927f3e3108bd7090d","tid":1016294,"uid":99568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:52:11.000Z","msg":"美式足球喺連登冇人理"},{"pid":"9b52abb2d6357d3075dc3c306accb0858cb8b2a4","tid":1016294,"uid":35286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"964ebc77b404a754598af3d927f3e3108bd7090d","tid":1016294,"uid":99568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:52:11.000Z","msg":"美式足球喺連登冇人理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:02:36.000Z","msg":"你想傾埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c358bba7707db4302c97f7165b8a76261ae2360d","tid":1016294,"uid":35286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:18:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>美式足球喺連登冇人理</blockquote>你想傾<span style=\"color: red;\">咩</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}